      <section class="mb-12">
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Ramadan bazaars and pasar malam nights are intense short-run businesses. Vendors operate with razor-thin margins for 30 days and must control every input cost — rent, ingredients, gas cylinders, and packaging. Used carton boxes from Quinocycle let bazaar traders across Selangor stock up on stall organisation, customer takeaway, and end-of-night breakdown packaging for a fraction of new-box pricing.</p>
