        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Family buyers ordering 10–20 pieces of pastry, kuih, or nasi bungkus don't want to juggle flimsy plastic bags. A small used carton with a rope handle keeps orders upright and looks more professional than random plastic bundles.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">End-of-Night Pack Up</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Unsold stock, utensils, and takeaway packaging all need to travel home each night. A stack of used cartons turns a chaotic tear-down into a 15-minute load-out. Stack them flat when empty — they take almost no van space.</p>
      </section>

